## Generic instructions:

make sure to follow standards and rules of the selected framework.

Create a .md file under "docs" folder for each module and list every functionality/feature added to the project.

manage all type/type def under a folder called "types" in root directory.

make sure to write/update each file fully, I don't want comments like "// ... rest of the code remains the same".

## backend instructions:

OpenAPI spec support with example request and response is must when working with backend/APIs.

write proper js docs when working with backend.

## frontend instructions:

Make webpages that are fully featured and worthy for production.

Use stock photos from unsplash where appropriate.